name: rb-jekyll-coffeescript
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "jekyll-coffeescript" %}
{% set version = "2.0.0" %}

package:
  name: rb-{{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://rubygems.org/downloads/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.gem
  sha256: 329c72fb62843056a5d6711514d4ff7f17a799169e88167d1d3a83ea1698d29d

build:
  noarch: generic
  number: 0
  script:
    - gem install -N -l -V --norc --ignore-dependencies {{ name }}-{{ version }}.gem
  skip: {{ win }}

requirements:
  host:
    - ruby
  run:
    - ruby
    - rb-coffee-script >=2.2,<3
    - rb-coffee-script-source >=1.12,<2

test:
  requires:
    - rb-jekyll >=3,<4
  commands:
    - ruby -r jekyll -r {{ name }} -e 'exit 0'

about:
  home: https://rubygems.org/gems/{{ name }}
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: A CoffeeScript converter for Jekyll

  doc_url: https://www.rubydoc.info/gems/{{ name }}
  dev_url: https://github.com/jekyll/{{ name }}

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - sodre
